data.description: Welcome to your dream waterfront home in Leisure Beach, Hudson, Florida! This stunning 3-bedroom, 2.5 bath oasis is situated in a peaceful cul-de-sac, offering the perfect blend of tranquility and luxury.    As you step inside, you'll be greeted by a wide open floor plan that seamlessly connects the living spaces. The kitchen is a chef's delight, boasting granite countertops and newer state-of-the-art stainless steel appliances. Imagine preparing meals with a view of the water just beyond your windows.    One of the highlights of this home is its commitment to sustainability, featuring newer solar panels to harness the power of the Florida sun.    Live the paradise lifestyle with your very own boat lift right at you backdoor. With a stationary dock and a separate floating dock, you have the perfect setup for enjoying waterfront living to the fullest. Picture yourself sipping a cup of coffee or enjoying a sunset right from your own backyard.    Leisure Beach is not just a neighborhood; it's a community that comes together for boat parades, golf cart parades, and a monthly "Coffee in the Cul-De-Sac" event during the colder months. It's the perfect opportunity to meet and connect with your neighbors.    You're only minutes away from fantastic restaurants like Skinny's, Ollie's, and Inn on the Gulf. The local Moose Lodge, and Eagles Lodge are also located right at the entrance to the community. For the fishing enthusiasts, the Gulf is just a short 5-minute boat ride from your backdoor, offering some of the best fishing in Florida. Anclote Island is also within reach, only a 25-minute boat ride away so you can enjoy those beautiful sunny Florida days on the white sandy beach that the island has to offer.    Take advantage of the convenience of docking your boat at several waterfront restaurants and indulge in the coastal lifestyle that Leisure Beach has to offer. Don't miss the chance to make this waterfront haven your home and start living the Florida waterfront lifestyle you've always dreamed of!
